name: Falex-vidal-official-website-2015
tagline: My own website portfolio and projects, using Wordpress, HTML5, CSS3 and jQuery. I think there might something useful for you here.
body:
### Falex Vidal Official Web Site

This website was constructed in 2015 as a part of an effort to put some portfolio stuff on line. It took up to 4 days to be complete and it's still a work in progress. There are some things that are still buggy and some things that need to be improved. If you wanna help me, feel free to collaborate with that project.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
